Enum ShapeNodeShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ShapeNodeShape>
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles.ShapeNodeShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ShapeNodeShape>

    public enum ShapeNodeShape
extends Enum<ShapeNodeShape>
    This enumeration predefines some often used shapes that can be used together with ShapeNodeStyle instances.
